ks and stay focussed on the big picture. Love to dive into the technology aspect of a program, gaining rich context that enables you to be even more thoughtful and effective in making the initiative happen.Drive the business forward through the programs you runStellar communication skills, both verbal and writtenKnowledge of studio production is a plus ","H2",null,[]],["Your EnvironmentYou will be trusted by your team and the organization to make impactful decisions. We also provide support through mentorship and coaching.You will contribute to a safe and inclusive environment by being curious and vulnerable.We will learn how to build the best creative experience together.For more information on what it’s like to work at Netflix, please take a look at our culture memo!Share this listing:         LINK COPIEDAPPLY NOW ","H2",null,[]],["Share this listing:         LINK COPIED
